    <text>
        <body>
            <opener><dateline><date when="1915-02-02">Feb. 2, 1915.</dateline></date>
                <salute>Dear <persName key="richard_aldington">Richard</persName>:</salute></opener>
            <p>This will introduce you to our publisher, <persName key="ferris_greenslet">Mr. Ferris Greenslet</persName>, who is most anxious to
                meet you. I only wish I were in his place and we were going to have one of our good times
                together. I know that he would like to meet <persName key="hilda_doolittle">Hilda</persName> too, and <persName key="fs_flint">Flint</persName> if you can arrange it. He has
                been so kind to us and so nice about our work that I am sure you will both enjoy meeting each
                other.</p>
            <closer><p>With love to Hilda and you from both <persName key="ada_russell">Mrs. Russell</persName> and myself,</p>
                <p>Affectionately yours,</p></closer>
        </body>
